data.description: Immaculate four-bedroom house is built for fun. Huge island kitchen features stainless steel appliances, a butler's pantry with extra cabinet space, large pantry, gas cooking and granite counters ready for barstools. Whirlpool two-drawer refrigerator included! The garage can be a party room with its epoxy floor, corrugated metal and wood trim and LED lights! Better than new! Enjoy the outside with a beautifully landscaped front yard and expanded driveway for easy parking. Covered patio in the back with fresh sod. The front bedroom can be a study. Enjoy extras like an art niche off the kitchen and decorative mirrored cabinets in the hall bathroom. This pristine property is ready for new owners in a neighborhood with great schools and plenty of amenities.
